725260f-a.title: Queens: 37th Avenue - 114th Street
725260f-a.text:
Thirty-seventh Avenue, foreground between 114th and 117th
Streets, showing in the background, viewing northward the Dr.
Corbes Sanatorium on the north side of Thirty-fourth Avenue,
between 114th and Wilcox Streets.
May 1920
Sugene L. Armbruster Collection

726644f-c.title: Queens: 114th Street - 37th Avenue
726644f-c.text:
Flushing Meadow Park: Woe1d's Fair Grounds. A set of
4 views. View number one is taken from 114th Street and Thirty-

TRirty-ninth Avenue; view number 3 from 114th Street and Roosevelt
